  "1463090": {
    "name": "《猎人：荒野的召唤™》蒂阿拉罗瓦国家公园",
    "steam_appid": 1463090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/9910070a9bdd7d33a6aae422c7c1cd9b.avif?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>蒂阿拉罗瓦国家公园有一种神奇的魅力，吸引了一代又一代的电影导演和猎人。连绵起伏的山丘、温带雨林和落叶林交错，是新西兰整个南岛的一个缩影。当你跋涉于这片美丽的自然保护区时，你会发现这里的景色变化万千，迷人不已。 <br><br>除了来蒂阿拉罗瓦国家公园找寻梅花鹿、臆羚和野山羊的猎人外，由于近年在这里拍摄的一些电影的缘故，这里还迎来了大量的游客。你和监督官凯丽·泰勒要确保保护区的美丽风景不会受到永久性的破坏，保证当地的动植物能够得到保护。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/855a2b81f6f493466b6fd62c87304556.webp?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/e4100d868213579d31354d031c0f7917.poster.avif?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/e4100d868213579d31354d031c0f7917.webm?t=1732025159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/e4100d868213579d31354d031c0f7917.mp4?t=1732025159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>蒂阿拉罗瓦风光旖旎，变化万千，猎人们尤其喜欢在这里追猎各种各样的动物。有些猎人是为了在山毛榉林中追逐珍贵的梅花鹿而来到这里，而另一些则是希望能一睹罕见的野猪、野山羊和臆羚的风采。对于那些寻求更轻松的体验的猎人来说，这里有大量的赤鹿、火鸡、欧洲野兔和黃鹿可供狩猎。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/0c067efda0fa58e3d2ddbd9ac837a132.webp?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/b53d632582a74e8089d5798364bac940.avif?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>蒂阿拉罗瓦常被用来描绘童话世界，这一点也不奇怪，因为它永不停息变化的生态系统确实令人无比赞叹。从将保护区一分为二的巍峨陡峭的山脉，到闪闪发光的海滩和茂密的温带森林，可以说是一步一景。这儿也有更普通的狩猎场，如云杉林和松树林。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/f790ad1bf263a700f9b8e91c198e9fa3.webp?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/c2e9a88fdd03f4a3056fe7d0ac67b6f4.poster.avif?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/c2e9a88fdd03f4a3056fe7d0ac67b6f4.webm?t=1732025159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/c2e9a88fdd03f4a3056fe7d0ac67b6f4.mp4?t=1732025159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>虽然这把fl Sporter .303保养状况不佳，但性能上一点都不逊色。栓式枪机平稳而可靠，易于更换弹药，适用于狩猎和打靶。可选的瞄具范围广泛，并且有效射程上佳，它可以轻松用于猎杀许多种动物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/b932dc43a6e219bb721103c49daa2fac.webp?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/f3d8a0ff7f3488b8dc9d6bcdbe13de4d.avif?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>蒂阿拉罗瓦国家公园占地25平方英里（64平方公里），不论是对于第一批迁徙到这里的波利尼西亚人，还是因从直升机上猎鹿而得名的彪悍猎人来说，这里一直是一个世外桃源。时局艰难，在监督官凯丽·泰勒勉强同意在保护区拍摄一系列好莱坞电影之后，这里几乎在一夜之间从无人问津的角落变成了一日游的热点。 <br><br>现在，保护区脆弱的生态受到了威胁，凯丽不能再坐视了。有你在身边，她将向全世界展示新西兰有的不仅仅是毛利族的战舞和半身人。在16个新的故事任务中，你将面对当地的威胁，修复老朋友之间的关系，并发现一个遗忘已久的传说背后的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/3836c4e07e8fa04f8a5e17dd21c677a3.webp?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463090/extras/5ce1ddff1842bdaf332692f560be4938.avif?t=1732025159\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br>即使你没有此DLC，也可以加入拥有DLC玩家的多人游戏中，体验在蒂阿拉罗瓦国家公园狩猎的精彩。通过这种方式，你将能获得除故事任务之外的全部体验。 ",
